Now Trump's White House is targeting the Freedom Statue.
The most reliable sign of regime change is when he starts fighting the statues.
The Americans understand this as well as everyone else -- from here to the deliberate theatrical demolition of Saddam Hussein's statue at Firdos Square in Baghdad in 2003.
Stephen Miller, one of Trump’s key ideologues, no doubt knew what he was doing when he brought the symbolic ax over the Statue of Liberty during a violent dispute with CNN journalist Jim Acosta about the President’s proposals to drastically reduce legal migration.
